    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. Every surface, mechanical component, and aesthetic detail has been preserved to an exacting degree. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence, this offering represents a definitive benchmark in quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 46500.0,
