    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, without hyperbole, a showroom-fresh example that will satisfy the most discerning collector. The exterior is finished in a flawless Deep Sea Blue Metallic, preserved by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a deep, mirror-like shine with zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the Ivory Nappa leather is supple and unmarked, retaining its original factory scent, while the genuine wood trim is free of any hairline scratches. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been maintained strictly according to manufacturer intervals with a complete, documented service history. Every feature, from the adaptive suspension to the premium surround-sound system, functions perfectly. This vehicle has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. It represents a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its absolute peak form.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
